{
  "title": "Robust Crispy Peruvian Beef Lomo Saltado",
  "description": "A malty and crispy Peruvian dish featuring beef strips, served with pistachio-free seasonings, perfect for a show-off dinner, this nut-free-friendly lomo saltado is a must-try",
